}}'''Brazil''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, Brasilia, along with Belo Horizonte, Curitiba, Fortaleza, Goiania,  Manaus, Porto Alegre, Recife, Rio de Janeiro, Salvador, Santos,  and São Paulo.
